	<h1 class="title">食物被扔掉，是因为变质还是因为你觉得它变质了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/26306/small/26306.jpg?1455710291" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">宣海伦</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-28 08:24:48 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5624/medium/5624.jpg?1436688878" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="5624" data-title="《食物被扔掉，是因为变质还是因为你觉得它变质了？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/5624/medium/5624.jpg?1436688878" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/5624" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
